post.description:
Authentication: send requests with the `X-API-Key` header for the target project.

Supported event types:

* `manual_service.request`  create a manual service request record.
* `customer_info.update`  update visitor profile using provided customer data.
* `customer_sentiment.update`  update visitor sentiment metrics.

`manual_service.request` payload schema:

```json
{
  "event_type": "manual_service.request",
  "visitor_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee",
  "payload": {
    "reason": "User explicitly requested to talk to a human agent.",
    "urgency": "high",
    "channel": "phone",
    "notification_type": "sms",
    "session_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee-vtr@251",
    "metadata": {
      "conversation_id": "conv-12345",
      "transcript_excerpt": "Please transfer me to a human."
    }
  }
}
```

`customer_info.update` payload schema:

```json
{
  "event_type": "customer_info.update",
  "visitor_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee",
  "payload": {
    "session_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee-vtr@251",
    "customer": {
      "extra_info": {
        "telegram": "@example_user",
        "preferences": {
          "language": "zh-CN"
        }
      },
      "email": "user@example.com",
      "phone": "+1-555-1234",
      "wechat": "wx123",
      "company": "Example Corp."
    },
    "metadata": {
      "conversation_id": "conv-67890"
    }
  }
}
```

Any keys nested under `customer.extra_info` are merged into the visitor's `custom_attributes`.

`customer_sentiment.update` payload schema:

```json
{
  "event_type": "customer_sentiment.update",
  "visitor_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee",
  "payload": {
    "session_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-cccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee-vtr@251",
    "sentiment": {
      "satisfaction": 4,
      "emotion": 5,
      "intent": "purchase"
    },
    "metadata": {
      "conversation_id": "conv-98765"
    }
  }
}
```
